!!! 5
html(lang='en')
	head
		title Acton authentication example
	body
		h1 Sign-in to this Acton site
		p Use <i>user</i> for the username and <i>pass</i> for the password.
		form(method='post')
			p
				label(for='username') Username
				input(type='text', name='username')
			p
				label(for='password') Password
				input(type='password', name='password')
				input(type='hidden', name='path', value='#{thirdParty}')
			input(type='submit')
		- each message in flash
			h4(style="color: red;") #{message}
